{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":273,"text":"We are at a remarkable moment in time."},{"time":4298,"text":"We face over the next two decades"},{"time":7234,"text":"two fundamental transformations"},{"time":9300,"text":"that will determine whether the next 100 years"},{"time":12342,"text":"is the best of centuries or the worst of centuries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":16527,"text":"Let me illustrate with an example."},{"time":19249,"text":"I first visited Beijing 25 years ago"},{"time":22523,"text":"to teach at the People's University of China."},{"time":25549,"text":"China was getting serious about market economics"},{"time":28485,"text":"and about university education,"},{"time":30824,"text":"so they decided to call in the foreign experts."},{"time":35315,"text":"Like most other people,"},{"time":36920,"text":"I moved around Beijing by bicycle."},{"time":39736,"text":"Apart from dodging the occasional vehicle,"},{"time":41930,"text":"it was a safe and easy way to get around."},{"time":45237,"text":"Cycling in Beijing now"},{"time":46601,"text":"is a completely different prospect."},{"time":49422,"text":"The roads are jammed by cars and trucks."},{"time":52565,"text":"The air is dangerously polluted"},{"time":54364,"text":"from the burning of coal and diesel."},{"time":57976,"text":"When I was there last in the spring,"},{"time":60114,"text":"there was an advisory for people of my age —"},{"time":62892,"text":"over 65 —"},{"time":65322,"text":"to stay indoors and not move much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68191,"text":"How did this come about?"},{"time":70125,"text":"It came from the way in which"},{"time":72545,"text":"Beijing has grown as a city."},{"time":74810,"text":"It's doubled over those 25 years, more than doubled,"},{"time":77270,"text":"from 10 million to 20 million."},{"time":79446,"text":"It's become a sprawling urban area"},{"time":81139,"text":"dependent on dirty fuel, dirty energy,"},{"time":85498,"text":"particularly coal."},{"time":87321,"text":"China burns half the world's coal each year,"},{"time":91596,"text":"and that's why, it is a key reason why,"},{"time":95510,"text":"it is the world's largest emitter"},{"time":97535,"text":"of greenhouse gases."},{"time":100449,"text":"At the same time, we have to recognize"},{"time":102563,"text":"that in that period China has grown remarkably."},{"time":105747,"text":"It has become the world's second largest economy."},{"time":108188,"text":"Hundreds of millions of people"},{"time":109657,"text":"have been lifted out of poverty."},{"time":111822,"text":"That's really important."},{"time":113903,"text":"But at the same time, the people of China"},{"time":116220,"text":"are asking the question:"},{"time":117820,"text":"What's the value of this growth"},{"time":119400,"text":"if our cities are unlivable?"},{"time":121525,"text":"They've analyzed, diagnosed"},{"time":123837,"text":"that this is an unsustainable path of growth"},{"time":127177,"text":"and development."},{"time":129303,"text":"China's planning to scale back coal."},{"time":131632,"text":"It's looking to build its cities in different ways."}]},{"cues":[{"time":137493,"text":"Now, the growth of China"},{"time":139326,"text":"is part of a dramatic change, fundamental change,"},{"time":143050,"text":"in the structure of the world economy."},{"time":145817,"text":"Just 25 years ago, the developing countries,"},{"time":148539,"text":"the poorer countries of the world,"},{"time":150429,"text":"were, notwithstanding being\nthe vast majority of the people,"},{"time":154355,"text":"they accounted for only about a third"},{"time":156178,"text":"of the world's output."},{"time":158170,"text":"Now it's more than half;"},{"time":159914,"text":"25 years from now, it will probably be two thirds"},{"time":162885,"text":"from the countries that we saw 25 years ago"},{"time":165990,"text":"as developing."},{"time":167266,"text":"That's a remarkable change."},{"time":168864,"text":"It means that most countries around the world,"},{"time":171266,"text":"rich or poor, are going to be facing"},{"time":173325,"text":"the two fundamental transformations"},{"time":175305,"text":"that I want to talk about and highlight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":178490,"text":"Now, the first of these transformations"},{"time":180503,"text":"is the basic structural change"},{"time":183110,"text":"of the economies and societies"},{"time":184850,"text":"that I've already begun to illustrate"},{"time":186880,"text":"through the description of Beijing."},{"time":190390,"text":"Fifty percent now in urban areas."},{"time":193349,"text":"That's going to go to 70 percent in 2050."},{"time":196960,"text":"Over the next two decades, we'll see"},{"time":199221,"text":"the demand for energy rise by 40 percent,"},{"time":202134,"text":"and the growth in the economy and in the population"},{"time":206108,"text":"is putting increasing pressure on our land,"},{"time":209090,"text":"on our water and on our forests."}]},{"cues":[{"time":212956,"text":"This is profound structural change."},{"time":216241,"text":"If we manage it in a negligent"},{"time":217816,"text":"or a shortsighted way,"},{"time":220435,"text":"we will create waste, pollution, congestion,"},{"time":224301,"text":"destruction of land and forests."},{"time":227851,"text":"If we think of those three areas that I have illustrated"},{"time":230179,"text":"with my numbers — cities, energy, land —"},{"time":233902,"text":"if we manage all that badly,"},{"time":235781,"text":"then the outlook for the lives and livelihoods"},{"time":237862,"text":"of the people around the world"},{"time":239673,"text":"would be poor and damaged."},{"time":242666,"text":"And more than that,"},{"time":244488,"text":"the emissions of greenhouse gases would rise,"},{"time":247796,"text":"with immense risks to our climate."},{"time":251677,"text":"Concentrations of greenhouse gases"},{"time":253724,"text":"in the atmosphere are already"},{"time":256642,"text":"higher than they've been for millions of years."},{"time":260276,"text":"If we go on increasing those concentrations,"},{"time":263914,"text":"we risk temperatures over the next century or so"},{"time":267288,"text":"that we have not seen on this planet"},{"time":268905,"text":"for tens of millions of years."},{"time":272110,"text":"We've been around as Homo sapiens —"},{"time":274236,"text":"that's a rather generous definition, sapiens —"},{"time":277407,"text":"for perhaps a quarter of a million\nyears, a quarter of a million."},{"time":280210,"text":"We risk temperatures we haven't seen"},{"time":281441,"text":"for tens of millions of years over a century."},{"time":286180,"text":"That would transform the relationship"},{"time":288250,"text":"between human beings and the planet."},{"time":292479,"text":"It would lead to changing deserts,"},{"time":297130,"text":"changing rivers, changing patterns of hurricanes,"},{"time":300320,"text":"changing sea levels,"},{"time":301558,"text":"hundreds of millions of people,"},{"time":304201,"text":"perhaps billions of people who would have to move,"},{"time":307430,"text":"and if we've learned anything from history,"},{"time":309353,"text":"that means severe and extended conflict."}]},{"cues":[{"time":311665,"text":"And we couldn't just turn it off."},{"time":313543,"text":"You can't make a peace treaty with the planet."},{"time":315973,"text":"You can't negotiate with the laws of physics."},{"time":318200,"text":"You're in there. You're stuck."},{"time":319915,"text":"Those are the stakes we're playing for,"},{"time":321591,"text":"and that's why we have to make\nthis second transformation,"},{"time":324313,"text":"the climate transformation,"},{"time":325953,"text":"and move to a low-carbon economy."},{"time":328336,"text":"Now, the first of these transformations"},{"time":330714,"text":"is going to happen anyway."},{"time":331795,"text":"We have to decide whether to do it well or badly,"},{"time":333644,"text":"the economic, or structural, transformation."},{"time":336462,"text":"But the second of the transformations,"},{"time":338352,"text":"the climate transformations, we have to decide to do."},{"time":342466,"text":"Those two transformations face us"},{"time":344685,"text":"in the next two decades."},{"time":346858,"text":"The next two decades are decisive"},{"time":350071,"text":"for what we have to do."},{"time":352786,"text":"Now, the more I've thought about this,"},{"time":354305,"text":"the two transformations coming together,"},{"time":356409,"text":"the more I've come to realize"},{"time":357956,"text":"that this is an enormous opportunity."},{"time":360908,"text":"It's an opportunity which we can use"},{"time":363135,"text":"or it's an opportunity which we can lose."},{"time":366532,"text":"And let me explain through those three key areas"},{"time":369255,"text":"that I've identified: cities, energy and land."},{"time":371965,"text":"And let me start with cities."},{"time":374019,"text":"I've already described the problems of Beijing:"},{"time":378052,"text":"pollution, congestion, waste and so on."},{"time":380898,"text":"Surely we recognize that in many of our cities"},{"time":384588,"text":"around the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":385847,"text":"Now, with cities, like life but particularly cities,"},{"time":388772,"text":"you have to think ahead."},{"time":391836,"text":"The cities that are going to be built —"},{"time":393250,"text":"and there are many, and many big ones —"},{"time":395406,"text":"we have to think of how to design them"},{"time":396870,"text":"in a compact way"},{"time":398221,"text":"so we can save travel time \nand we can save energy."},{"time":401664,"text":"The cities that already are \nthere, well established,"},{"time":405579,"text":"we have to think about renewal\nand investment in them"},{"time":408650,"text":"so that we can connect ourselves much better"},{"time":411428,"text":"within those cities, and make it easier,"},{"time":413820,"text":"encourage more people, to live closer to the center."},{"time":417411,"text":"We've got examples building around the world"},{"time":419821,"text":"of the kinds of ways in which we can do that."},{"time":422113,"text":"The bus rapid transport system in Bogotá in Colombia"},{"time":426131,"text":"is a very important case of how to move around"},{"time":428763,"text":"safely and quickly in a non-polluting way"},{"time":431333,"text":"in a city: very frequent buses,"},{"time":434528,"text":"strongly protected routes, the same service, really,"},{"time":437465,"text":"as an underground railway system,"},{"time":439556,"text":"but much, much cheaper"},{"time":441367,"text":"and can be done much more quickly,"},{"time":443775,"text":"a brilliant idea in many more cities"},{"time":445670,"text":"around the world that's developing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":447706,"text":"Now, some things in cities do take time."},{"time":449607,"text":"Some things in cities can happen much more quickly."},{"time":452660,"text":"Take my hometown, London."},{"time":454764,"text":"In 1952, smog in London killed 4,000 people"},{"time":460052,"text":"and badly damaged the lives of many, many more."},{"time":462746,"text":"And it happened all the time."},{"time":464096,"text":"For those of you live outside London in the U.K."},{"time":466598,"text":"will remember it used to be called The Smoke."},{"time":468791,"text":"That's the way London was."},{"time":470467,"text":"By regulating coal, within a few years"},{"time":472549,"text":"the problems of smog were rapidly reduced."},{"time":475637,"text":"I remember the smogs well."},{"time":477192,"text":"When the visibility dropped to [less] than"},{"time":479915,"text":"a few meters,"},{"time":481908,"text":"they stopped the buses and I had to walk."},{"time":483764,"text":"This was the 1950s."},{"time":485822,"text":"I had to walk home three miles from school."},{"time":489720,"text":"Again, breathing was a hazardous activity."},{"time":493289,"text":"But it was changed. It was changed by a decision."},{"time":495967,"text":"Good decisions can bring good results,"},{"time":499136,"text":"striking results, quickly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":501501,"text":"We've seen more: In London, we've\nintroduced the congestion charge,"},{"time":504494,"text":"actually quite quickly and effectively,"},{"time":507200,"text":"and we've seen great improvements"},{"time":508820,"text":"in the bus system, and cleaned up the bus system."},{"time":512782,"text":"You can see that the two\ntransformations I've described,"},{"time":515902,"text":"the structural and the climate,"},{"time":517858,"text":"come very much together."},{"time":520490,"text":"But we have to invest. We have to invest in our cities,"},{"time":523423,"text":"and we have to invest wisely, and if we do,"},{"time":525956,"text":"we'll see cleaner cities, quieter cities, safer cities,"},{"time":530492,"text":"more attractive cities, more productive cities,"},{"time":533149,"text":"and stronger community in those cities —"},{"time":535916,"text":"public transport, recycling, reusing,"},{"time":538164,"text":"all sorts of things that bring communities together."},{"time":542213,"text":"We can do that, but we have to think,"},{"time":544070,"text":"we have to invest, we have to plan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":546350,"text":"Let me turn to energy."},{"time":548521,"text":"Now, energy over the last 25 years"},{"time":551743,"text":"has increased by about 50 percent."},{"time":553979,"text":"Eighty percent of that comes from fossil fuels."},{"time":556596,"text":"Over the next 20 years,"},{"time":558254,"text":"perhaps it will increase by another 40 percent or so."},{"time":562030,"text":"We have to invest strongly in energy,"},{"time":564564,"text":"we have to use it much more efficiently,"},{"time":567838,"text":"and we have to make it clean."},{"time":569526,"text":"We can see how to do that."},{"time":570856,"text":"Take the example of California."},{"time":572760,"text":"It would be in the top 10 countries in the world"},{"time":575370,"text":"if it was independent."},{"time":577913,"text":"I don't want to start any —"},{"time":580478,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":583976,"text":"California's a big place."},{"time":585821,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":587869,"text":"In the next five or six years,"},{"time":590610,"text":"they will likely move from"},{"time":593324,"text":"around 20 percent in renewables —"},{"time":595563,"text":"wind, solar and so on —"},{"time":597320,"text":"to over 33 percent,"},{"time":599793,"text":"and that would bring California back"},{"time":602232,"text":"to greenhouse gas emissions in 2020"},{"time":604765,"text":"to where they were in 1990,"},{"time":606722,"text":"a period when the economy in California"},{"time":608466,"text":"would more or less have doubled."},{"time":609898,"text":"That's a striking achievement."},{"time":611348,"text":"It shows what can be done."},{"time":612831,"text":"Not just California — the \nincoming government of India"},{"time":616138,"text":"is planning to get solar technology"},{"time":619164,"text":"to light up the homes"},{"time":620536,"text":"of 400 million people"},{"time":622246,"text":"who don't have electricity in India."},{"time":624311,"text":"They've set themselves a target of five years."},{"time":626791,"text":"I think they've got a good chance of doing that."},{"time":630020,"text":"We'll see, but what you're seeing now"},{"time":632679,"text":"is people moving much more quickly."},{"time":634990,"text":"Four hundred million, more than the population"},{"time":636724,"text":"of the United States."},{"time":638850,"text":"Those are the kinds of ambitions now"},{"time":640943,"text":"people are setting themselves"},{"time":642649,"text":"in terms of rapidity of change."},{"time":647129,"text":"Again, you can see"},{"time":649099,"text":"good decisions can bring quick results,"},{"time":650880,"text":"and those two transformations,\nthe economy and the structure"},{"time":653913,"text":"and the climate and the low carbon,"},{"time":655904,"text":"are intimately intertwined."},{"time":658447,"text":"Do the first one well, the structural,"},{"time":660269,"text":"the second one on the climate"},{"time":662250,"text":"becomes much easier."}]},{"cues":[{"time":665432,"text":"Look at land,"},{"time":667221,"text":"land and particularly forests."},{"time":669809,"text":"Forests are the hosts to valuable"},{"time":672869,"text":"plant and animal species."},{"time":675398,"text":"They hold water in the soil"},{"time":677746,"text":"and they take carbon dioxide out of the atmosphere,"},{"time":680664,"text":"fundamental to the tackling of climate change."},{"time":683733,"text":"But we're losing our forests."},{"time":685965,"text":"In the last decade, we've lost a forest area"},{"time":688792,"text":"the size of Portugal,"},{"time":690935,"text":"and much more has been degraded."},{"time":693398,"text":"But we're already seeing"},{"time":695153,"text":"that we can do so much about that."},{"time":697560,"text":"We can recognize the problem, but we can also"},{"time":699597,"text":"understand how to tackle it."},{"time":701711,"text":"In Brazil, the rate of deforestation"},{"time":704366,"text":"has been reduced by 70 percent"},{"time":706383,"text":"over the last 10 years."},{"time":708945,"text":"How? By involving local communities,"},{"time":711930,"text":"investing in their agriculture and their economies,"},{"time":714751,"text":"by monitoring more carefully,"},{"time":716851,"text":"by enforcing the law more strictly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":720496,"text":"And it's not just stopping deforestation."},{"time":722386,"text":"That's of course of first and fundamental importance,"},{"time":724827,"text":"but it's also regrading degraded land,"},{"time":728449,"text":"regenerating, rehabilitating degraded land."},{"time":732849,"text":"I first went to Ethiopia in 1967."},{"time":736729,"text":"It was desperately poor. In the following years,"},{"time":739204,"text":"it suffered devastating famines"},{"time":740950,"text":"and profoundly destructive social conflict."},{"time":744806,"text":"Over the last few years, actually more than a few,"},{"time":747640,"text":"Ethiopia has been growing much more rapidly."},{"time":750565,"text":"It has ambitions to be a middle-income country"},{"time":752455,"text":"15 years from now"},{"time":754960,"text":"and to be carbon neutral."},{"time":757203,"text":"Again, I think it's a strong ambition"},{"time":760251,"text":"but it is a plausible one."},{"time":762546,"text":"You're seeing that commitment there."},{"time":763957,"text":"You're seeing what can be done."},{"time":765223,"text":"Ethiopia is investing in clean energy."},{"time":767788,"text":"It's working in the rehabilitation of land."},{"time":771410,"text":"In Humbo, in southwest Ethiopia,"},{"time":773840,"text":"a wonderful project"},{"time":775257,"text":"to plant trees on degraded land"},{"time":777440,"text":"and work with local communities"},{"time":779060,"text":"on sustainable forest management"},{"time":781509,"text":"has led to big increases in living standards."}]},{"cues":[{"time":784550,"text":"So we can see, from Beijing to London,"},{"time":788414,"text":"from California to India,"},{"time":790703,"text":"from Brazil to Ethiopia,"},{"time":793830,"text":"we do understand"},{"time":795439,"text":"how to manage those two transformations,"},{"time":797644,"text":"the structural and the climate."},{"time":799573,"text":"We do understand how to manage those well."},{"time":803752,"text":"And technology is changing very rapidly."},{"time":806530,"text":"I don't have to list all those things"},{"time":808937,"text":"to an audience like this,"},{"time":810828,"text":"but you can see the electric cars,"},{"time":813122,"text":"you can see the batteries using new materials."},{"time":816206,"text":"You can see that we can manage remotely now"},{"time":818601,"text":"our household appliances on our\nmobile phones when we're away."},{"time":822156,"text":"You can see better insulation."},{"time":823963,"text":"And there's much more coming."}]},{"cues":[{"time":825886,"text":"But, and it's a big but,"},{"time":828283,"text":"the world as a whole"},{"time":829892,"text":"is moving far too slowly."},{"time":832670,"text":"We're not cutting emissions in the way we should."},{"time":835212,"text":"We're not managing those structural transformations"},{"time":837923,"text":"as we can."},{"time":840152,"text":"The depth of understanding of the\nimmense risks of climate change"},{"time":843391,"text":"are not there yet."},{"time":846970,"text":"The depth of understanding"},{"time":849101,"text":"of the attractiveness of what we can do"},{"time":851586,"text":"is not there yet."},{"time":855250,"text":"We need political pressure to build."},{"time":858748,"text":"We need leaders to step up."},{"time":862280,"text":"We can have better growth,"},{"time":865779,"text":"better climate, a better world."},{"time":869986,"text":"We can make,"},{"time":871798,"text":"by managing those two transformations well,"},{"time":874578,"text":"the next 100 years the best of centuries."},{"time":878866,"text":"If we make a mess of it,"},{"time":880093,"text":"we, you and me, if we make a mess of it,"},{"time":883240,"text":"if we don't manage those transformations properly,"},{"time":885713,"text":"it will be, the next 100 years"},{"time":888604,"text":"will be the worst of centuries."},{"time":891335,"text":"That's the major conclusion"},{"time":893227,"text":"of the report on the economy and climate"},{"time":896358,"text":"chaired by ex-President Felipe Calderón of Mexico,"},{"time":900227,"text":"and I co-chaired that with him,"},{"time":902407,"text":"and we handed that report yesterday"},{"time":904360,"text":"here in New York, in the United Nations Building"},{"time":907350,"text":"to the Secretary-General of the U.N.,"},{"time":908822,"text":"Ban Ki-moon."},{"time":910088,"text":"We know that we can do this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":914193,"text":"Now, two weeks ago,"},{"time":917575,"text":"I became a grandfather for the fourth time."},{"time":920975,"text":"Our daughter —"},{"time":923107,"text":"(Baby cries) (Laughter) (Applause) —"},{"time":933710,"text":"Our daughter gave birth to Rosa here in New York"},{"time":936621,"text":"two weeks ago. Here are Helen and Rosa."},{"time":939626,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":946870,"text":"Two weeks old."},{"time":949838,"text":"Are we going to look our grandchildren in the eye"},{"time":955525,"text":"and tell them that we understood the issues,"},{"time":959272,"text":"that we recognized the dangers and the opportunities,"},{"time":962590,"text":"and still we failed to act?"},{"time":966831,"text":"Surely not. Let's make the next 100 years"},{"time":970310,"text":"the best of centuries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":972116,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}